{"tid":1536741,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[拋磚引玉] 我係罷買救港發起人之一，上個月我罷買省左少少錢，捐左比星火，有冇人挑機","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:41:57.000Z","uid":58883,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09032618fd608cc78d30c42a9fc7ecf006a6019d","tid":1536741,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VC727RM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVC727RM.jpg&h=fe94c34d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發起左罷買行動之後，省埋省埋Ｄ錢捐左比星火，想拋磚引玉，但係得我一個唔夠？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我打算係facebook發起Challenge，呼籲facebook audience 跟機(有25+ followers，主要係中年有少少錢既和理非)。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地希望更多人可以嚮應罷買／一齊捐錢幫義士。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果你地聽日之前捐完，請blur個人資訊pm我地 Byebuyday fb/ig/tg (下面有) ，我會將大家既收據大約星期五一次過放上FB去challenge班和理非。</strong><br />\n<em>向星火捐款途徑:<br />\n滙豐銀行: 048-857585-838 <br />\n戶口全名: The Prime Management Service Ltd.<br />\n自動櫃員機戶口名字顯示: T PR**E M*L T*A T*C <br />\n轉數快ID: 3771623</em><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">佢地FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/sparkalliancehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fsparkalliancehk&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=00d8d05a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/sparkalliancehk</a></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8x4XWN0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8x4XWN0.jpg&h=30c16670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罷買係星星之火，我相信大家一齊去做會好有效果<br />\n______________________________________<br />\n簽署承諾罷買︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ORv5Zw&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=0fd23da0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw</a><br />\nfacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/p